  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个工业物联网场景下的ARP协议序列图，展示PLC逻辑控制器如何通过交换机与边缘节点通信。场景里有四台设备：A和D是PLC逻辑单元，B是遥测流节点，C是边缘节点，中间通过一个支持遥测流的交换机连接。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Computadora A",
        "Computadora B",
        "Computadora C",
        "Computadora D",
        "Switch",
        "IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic",
        "IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream",
        "IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，这是一个典型的工业现场网络拓扑。我确认一下：A和D都是PLC逻辑控制器，但A是发起通信的一方，D只是同类型的另一台设备？还有交换机一开始MAC表是空的，对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Switch",
        "IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic",
        "Note"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的，交换机初始状态MAC表为空。A要发数据给C，但不知道C的MAC地址，所以触发ARP流程。D在这个场景里主要是作为对比——它也会收到广播，但不会响应。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Computadora A",
        "Computadora C",
        "Computadora D",
        "ARP",
        "Broadcast"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先画出五个参与者：A（标注为IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic）、交换机（IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream）、B（IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream）、C（IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode）、D（IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic）。然后在交换机上方加注释说明MAC表为空。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Computadora A",
        "Switch",
        "Computadora B",
        "Computadora C",
        "Computadora D",
        "Note"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "接下来进入第一阶段：ARP请求。这里有个关键细节——A发出的ARP请求需要标注它来自TelemetryStream，目标是广播到EdgeNode。这体现了我们MQTT Broker层的设计。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Computadora A",
        "Switch",
        "ARP Request",
        "IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream",
        "IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode",
        "IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "我注意到您提到MQTT Broker，但ARP是二层协议，这里标注MQTT Broker是为了说明什么？是表示这个ARP请求会被MQTT Broker处理，还是只是阶段标识？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ARP Request",
        "IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是阶段标识。我们用\"FASE 1: ARP Request (IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker)\"这样的注释横跨A和D，表示这个请求阶段属于MQTT Broker通信的建立过程。实际ARP帧还是标准格式。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Note",
        "Computadora A",
        "Computadora D",
        "IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "理解了，我在A和D上方加了阶段注释。现在画A到交换机的ARP请求箭头，标注源是A（TelemetryStream），目标是广播（EdgeNode）。然后交换机要学到A的MAC在端口1。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Computadora A",
        "Switch",
        "ARP Request",
        "Note",
        "MAC"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "很好，接下来交换机把ARP请求泛洪出去。注意B、C、D三台设备都会收到，但我在注释里要说明\"Solo C responde al ARP\"——因为只有C是边缘节点需要被访问，B和D忽略这个请求。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Switch",
        "Computadora B",
        "Computadora C",
        "Computadora D",
        "ARP Request"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "画好了，交换机到B、C、D三条ARP Request箭头。B和D的箭头标注为PLC_Logic和TelemetryStream，C的是EdgeNode。然后在B和D上方加注释说明只有C会响应。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Switch",
        "Computadora B",
        "Computadora C",
        "Computadora D",
        "ARP Request",
        "Note",
        "IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic",
        "IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream",
        "IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "进入第二阶段：ARP响应。C知道是找自己的，单播回应给A。这里响应要标注来自MQTT Broker，目标是ActuatorController——表示这是控制通道的确认。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Computadora C",
        "Computadora A",
        "ARP Response",
        "IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker",
        "IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "确认一下，ActuatorController在这里是指A的角色吗？因为A是PLC逻辑控制器，应该具备执行控制能力。还是说这是一个独立的组件？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Computadora A",
        "IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController",
        "IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "ActuatorController就是A的功能角色，PLC_Logic是它的设备类型。所以标注\"Destino: A (IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController)\"是准确的。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Computadora A",
        "IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController",
        "IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 14,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "明白了。我添加阶段注释\"FASE 2: ARP Response\"，然后画C到交换机的ARP响应，标注源C（MQTT Broker）目标A（ActuatorController）。交换机学到C在端口3。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Computadora C",
        "Switch",
        "Computadora A",
        "ARP Response",
        "Note",
        "IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker",
        "IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 15,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "等等，我刚才的执行有问题。让我修正：C到交换机的ARP响应标注应该是源C（MQTT Broker），但交换机转发给A的时候，箭头标注应该是PLC_Logic而不是保持ActuatorController，因为这时是网络层交付。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Switch",
        "Computadora A",
        "ARP Response",
        "IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 16,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "修正得对。交换机到A的ARP响应标注为PLC_Logic，表示这是给PLC逻辑控制器的网络层交付。现在可以进入第三阶段了：直接数据通信。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Switch",
        "Computadora A",
        "ARP Response",
        "IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 17,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "添加\"FASE 3: Comunicación Directa\"注释。现在A有C的MAC了，可以直接发数据。我画A到交换机的数据箭头，标注\"Datos para C\"，源A（MQTT Broker）目标C（MQTT Broker）。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Computadora A",
        "Switch",
        "Computadora C",
        "Datos",
        "Note",
        "IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 18,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "数据包的源和目标都标MQTT Broker，这是表示应用层封装吗？但数据帧本身的MAC层应该是A到C的直接寻址。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Computadora A",
        "Computadora C",
        "Datos",
        "IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker",
        "MAC"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 19,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的，这里的MQTT Broker标注表示这是MQTT应用层的数据流，MAC层寻址已经在ARP阶段完成。交换机现在查表知道C在端口3，直接单播转发。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Switch",
        "Computadora C",
        "Datos",
        "IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker",
        "MAC"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 20,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "最后一步，交换机转发数据给C。这个箭头标注为TelemetryStream，表示数据最终到达边缘节点的遥测处理模块。整个流程体现了从广播学习到精准转发的完整过程。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Switch",
        "Computadora C",
        "Datos",
        "IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 21,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "完成。我添加了交换机上的注释\"Consulta tabla MAC, Encuentra C en puerto 3\"，然后画交换机到C的数据箭头，标注TelemetryStream。整个序列图现在完整展示了ARP学习和数据转发的三个阶段。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Switch",
        "Computadora C",
        "Datos",
        "Note",
        "IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream",
        "MAC"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 22,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "我再看一眼，B和D的角色标注在ARP请求阶段是不是有点混淆？B标注为PLC_Logic，但B实际上是TelemetryStream节点，让我确认一下之前的设定。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Computadora B",
        "IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic",
        "IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 23,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "您说得对，我需要修正。交换机到B的ARP请求应该保持为TelemetryStream，不是PLC_Logic。让我调整：S-B箭头标注为ARP Request (IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream)，S-D才是PLC_Logic。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Switch",
        "Computadora B",
        "Computadora D",
        "ARP Request",
        "IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream",
        "IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 24,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "完美，现在逻辑一致了。A和D是PLC_Logic，B和C分别是TelemetryStream和EdgeNode，交换机是TelemetryStream设备。整个图准确反映了工业物联网中控制层、传输层和边缘层的交互。可以定稿了。",
      "elements_involved": [
